messages.subject: pet vaccinations
messages.messageBody:
<<I don't want to give her anything more than is absolutely legally
required.>>

This is what we do. I take them to a vet and say "Just make them legal."
Here in Texas it is just a rabies vaccination and I am only doing that
because our psycho lab/dalmation mix will be attending dog obedience classes
next week.

As far as a vet, we have been happiest with a vet that is used to dealing
with farm animals. We called the county extension agent and asked if they
knew of any vets in our area that gave price breaks to FFA and 4-H kids. We
couldn't be happier.

Julie
